# RAG Eval Kit — example environment variables
#
# The core library has zero runtime dependencies and requires no API keys.
# If you extend the toolkit to call a vector database or LLM API, add those
# credentials here and load them with python-dotenv or os.environ.
#
# Example — Pinecone vector database:
# PINECONE_API_KEY=your-key-here
# PINECONE_ENVIRONMENT=us-east-1-aws
#
# Example — OpenAI for generating embeddings:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values. Never commit .env to git.
